precis:
Enactment of the INSIDER REPORTS EXEMPTIONS (BANKS) REGULATIONS which
exempt an insider from having to file reports with the Office of the
Superintendent of Financial Institutions if they have already been filed
with any of the provincial or territorial securities commissions.
